about.summary: Collection of utilities, scripts and tests to assist in automated quality assurance.

name: ioos_qartod
raw_recipe:
{% set version = "0.0.3" %}

package:
    name: ioos_qartod
    version: {{ version }}

source:
    fn: ioos_qartod-{{ version }}.tar.gz
    url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/i/ioos_qartod/ioos_qartod-{{ version }}.tar.gz
    sha256: 2936e09437b8ed3e555aef9cb69625da89e6a228e403684a57fc521c08521d67

build:
    number: 0
    script: python setup.py install --single-version-externally-managed --record record.txt

requirements:
    build:
        - python
        - setuptools
    run:
        - python
        - numpy
        - pandas
        - quantities
        - pyproj

test:
    imports:
        - ioos_qartod

about:
    home: https://pypi.python.org/pypi/ioos_qartod
    license: Apache 2.0
    summary: 'Collection of utilities, scripts and tests to assist in automated quality assurance.'

extra:
    recipe-maintainers:
        - ocefpaf
